Package: bizdays
Title: Functions to handle business days calculations
Description: bizdays is a small set of functions to help with calculations which
    make use of business days. Fixed income calculations in Brazil make intense
    use of that.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Wilson Freitas <wilson.freitas@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Wilson Freitas <wilson.freitas@gmail.com>
Depends:
    R (>= 2.15.1)
License: MIT
LazyData: true
Collate:
    'R-bizdays-package.r'
    'calendar.R'
